summary:
As a recruiter with many years of experience in the HR field, I have expertise in both strategic work and operational recruitment. My broad experience from previous positions at Nordea Corporate Adviser, Employer Branding, Graduate Program, and Executive Search gives me a unique ability to handle many different HR challenges. My strength lies in my ability to understand the organization's needs and to collaborate with different stakeholders and managers to find the best recruits. My goal is always to find employees who can help the company grow and stay for the long term.

I am particularly proud of my ability to collaborate with people at all levels of the organization. I enjoy working towards set goals and seeing things from different perspectives to find the best solutions. My experience and expertise make me a valuable resource for all HR-related questions, and I look forward to continuing to help companies build their teams successfully.
